                          PATENT-PENDING INNOVATIONS
================================================================================

This software contains patent-pending technology:

EVM PRECOMPILE INNOVATIONS:
- DEX Precompiles (Uniswap v4-Style Singleton PoolManager at 0x0400)
- Sub-Microsecond Swap Execution (2.26Î¼s, 443K ops/sec)
- Flash Accounting with Native EVM Integration
- Hooks Registry for Extensible Pool Behavior
- Native LUX Trading Without Wrapping

POST-QUANTUM CRYPTOGRAPHY PRECOMPILES:
- ML-DSA (Dilithium) Signature Verification (0x0300)
- NVTrust GPU Attestation for AI Mining
- BLS12-381 Operations (EIP-2537)
- BN254 ZK Precompiles (EIP-1108)

FHE PRECOMPILES:
- fhEVM Encrypted Computation Precompiles
- Ciphertext Storage and Retrieval
- Encrypted Arithmetic Operations

